<span id="freeTextContainer6578015557308066283">This memoir about a herd of &apos;rogue&apos; elephants and conservationist Lawrence on his reserve in Africa is feel-good and informative at the same time. The audiobook won an Audie and it is well deserved as it is a great listen. I thoroughly enjoyed this and would definitely recommend it.</span>
  <span id="freeText6578015557308066283" style="display:none">This memoir about a herd of 'rogue' elephants and conservationist Lawrence on his reserve in Africa is feel-good and informative at the same time. The audiobook won an Audie and it is well deserved as it is a great listen. I thoroughly enjoyed this and would definitely recommend it.</span>
